data.description: Gorgeous well-kept, one owner 3 bedroom 2 bath home recently built in the growing Saratoga addition. Featuring granite countertops, large kitchen island, open floorplan, double vanity primary bathroom with generously sized walk-in closet, spacious laundry room, and wood-look tile floors. The front office with French door entry is great for work-at home or a play room. Fridge conveys to complete the stainless steel kitchen appliance suite. Historic downtown and Lake Granbury are only 10 minutes away!
